== Overview ==
An EM Pulse Emitter generate periodic magnetic pulses that disperse incoming energy drain effects from enemy units.

== Where to Acquire ==
The EM Pulse Emitter can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
